<font color=#00FFFF>@elder_man</font>

20:30.513 --> 20:33.849
Thayson, Joshuel, don't make me
pick between you two

20:33.883 --> 20:36.518
on the night before I reenter
the Struggle Dome again.

20:36.552 --> 20:37.986
We'll never stop loving you,

20:38.020 --> 20:40.488
even if you string
us along forever.

20:40.523 --> 20:42.591
Forever.
Forever.

20:42.625 --> 20:45.160
How can I choose
between two boys,

20:45.194 --> 20:47.395
one who's dangerous
but good-looking,

20:47.430 --> 20:49.698
the other who's strong
but super cute?

20:49.732 --> 20:51.499
Ah!

20:51.534 --> 20:54.336
Oh, my God,
this is terrible.

20:54.370 --> 20:56.538
When do they get
to killing the children?

20:56.572 --> 20:57.873
Shh!

20:57.907 --> 20:59.774
Wait a second.
You're not into this...

20:59.809 --> 21:01.243
Shh!

21:01.277 --> 21:02.911
She's trying
on dresses.

21:02.945 --> 21:07.048
Oh, I just wanted to see kids
fight to the death, is all.

21:07.083 --> 21:09.718
Shh...!

21:52.471 --> 21:53.710
Shh!

